Module io.netty5.codec

    • Packages

      Exports 
      Package Description
      io.netty5.handler.codec
      Extensible decoder and its common implementations which deal with the packet fragmentation and reassembly issue found in a stream-based transport such as TCP/IP.
      io.netty5.handler.codec.base64
      Encoder and decoder which transform a Base64-encoded String or io.netty5.buffer.ByteBuf into a decoded io.netty5.buffer.ByteBuf and vice versa.
      io.netty5.handler.codec.bytes
      Encoder and decoder which transform an array of bytes into a io.netty5.buffer.ByteBuf and vice versa.
      io.netty5.handler.codec.compression
      Encoder and decoder which compresses and decompresses io.netty5.buffer.ByteBufs in a compression format such as zlib, gzip, and Snappy.
      io.netty5.handler.codec.string
      Encoder and decoder which transform a String into a io.netty5.buffer.ByteBuf and vice versa.
